{"tid":541072,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"新whatsapp group 搵廢青飯酒腳 識下朋友","createTime":"2018-01-26T05:27:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-08T00:06:29.000Z","uid":87503,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fdcdd995ea8104e58d22d2b3c2c0559b2bb28a46","tid":541072,"uid":87503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T05:27:55.000Z","msg":"想開一個whatsapp group 結合一班廢青<br />\n用whatsapp既原因係因為想大家成為生活上既朋友<br />\n如果介意既話禁上一頁走啦拜拜<br />\n<br />\n目標係有20個活躍份子 男女會盡量平均<br />\n識下朋友 得閒出黎飯聚／酒聚為主<br />\n同埋假期搞下其他活動<br />\n禁止厹／娘娘／煩膠／冇品／sales／美容，敬請自重<br />\n<br />\n認真填左呢張form先，夠人開group會whatsapp pm你<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSd0MLZs6r7TPLrvpYdbbbc3WQEia09LKN1T4duS-3GIKKEnDA/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSd0MLZs6r7TPLrvpYdbbbc3WQEia09LKN1T4duS-3GIKKEnDA%2Fviewform&d=6b8NNPeCEMRihft%2FqxBOAk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=acee0d86\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSd0MLZs6r7TPLrvpYdbbbc3WQEia09LKN1T4duS-3GIKKEnDA/viewform</a>"},{"pid":"2d003eba01f3552782deb3f6dba61a085ef7b09e","tid":541072,"uid":87503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T05:28:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"904216cc94a03ef54a6cccfc90d5cac25a76d85c","tid":541072,"uid":87503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T07:06:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f69c47111c5c9ec19b7a0e9a14bbb519aa32780","tid":541072,"uid":87503,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T07:09:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"853db6e6ee664b98a5fe98059a2412d272ffd479","tid":541072,"uid":87503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T10:17:22.000Z",